Class MvsMElements

  • java.lang.Object
    • MvsMElements

  • public class MvsMElements
extends java.lang.Object
    In this class the scene is created which is called by the class StartElements.
    It appears by pressing the M vs. M button from the StartElements class.
    Author:
    Benedikt Nork (1188594), Geraldine Denise Lengert (1186185), Robert Uwe Litschel (1183829), Nasim Ahmad (1185555)
